Package mathlib3D

Class Summary
Matrix3D Defines a 3D (4x4) matrix for general transformations.
MatrixInvert This class is a helper class supporting the Matrix3D class; it is not intended to be used directly.
Point3D Defines a three-dimensional homogeneous point.
Vector3D Defines a three-dimensional vector.
Vertex3D Defines a 3D polygon vertex.
